The Russian Ministry of Health authorized on Saturday the use of Sputnik V on people over 60 to immunize them against Covid-19, the capital’s television reported.According to Minister of Health Mikhail Murashko, experts confirmed it’s safe to inject Sputnik V to the aforementioned age group, which had not been included in the large scale vaccination started this month among risk groups. The first registered Covid-19 vaccine in the world was limited, for the time being, to a group from 18 to 60. In this capital, the vaccination of physicians, teachers, and social workers belonging to this age group started in November. For the time being, children and pregnant women are not included, for whom additional scientific studies are being conducted. In this city, besides the three aforementioned risk categories, other sectors such as transportation, commerce, industry, and media workers were also included. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! However, since last Thursday, communal services, food, sports, public order bodies, including the police, the attorney general’s office workers, judges and others will also be able to register on the official website of the mayor’s office. Russia has recorded 54,226 deaths due to Covid-19 to date, after reporting 567 deaths in a day, the general staff to fight this disease indicated. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION